desc: Programming dynamic React components for a student hub, facilitating local project discovery. Implementing user feedback to enhance style and functionality, optimizing user experience. Collaborating with the design team to bring the website to life through a fusion of design and functionality. Ensuring smooth frontend-to-database connection by working closely with the backend team.

Delivering weekly instruction to a cohort of 25-30 students on information systems and design. Collaborating with a dynamic teaching team to craft innovative course material and class organization. Providing comprehensive support by addressing student inquiries regarding course content and logistics.

Developed a web app that teaches coding, leveraging JavaScript and React framework. Collaborated with a team of 2 developers to create a Wizard of Oz app for testing. Engaged in insightful discussions on AI literacy with families and children, gaining deeper stakeholder understanding. Executed impactful community-based research with families, focusing on AI literacy for valuable insights.
